uld also drain mana from THEM.  In my version, it DOES stop offensive casting, so if this were also given to mobs, they would find themselves without offensive casting ability if the mob uses it.  It's a trade-off, use it and avoid magical damage at the cost of mana, leave it off and you may find your mana wasted on the other wizard that has it.<br>
<br>
In general, this would be a VERY interesting skill and would add layers and layers to the complexity of the class, both in PvP, as well as PvE.<br>
