<br>
Consider this the FIRST step, a caster version of dodge.<br>
<br>
The next would be a caster(preferably wizard only) reposte, where you not only can dodge, but automatically cast a low damage, low mana spell back at the opposing caster.  Again, this would be a skill, not a spell.  And would be something that would let the wizard act more as a caster that has been trained for battle.<br>
 <p>Targonis Manastorm<br>
